<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=+2>Chapter 9:&nbsp; Memory Management:Codecs</FONT></B></CENTER>

<CENTER>by</CENTER>

<CENTER><I>Bhaskaran Vasudev</I> and <I>Wei Li</I></CENTER>

